{
  "id": "8729e326e1c152d67fe936cb",
  "title": "日本之行",
  "summary": "蓄谋已久的日本之行。 东京 迪士尼遇到大雨，只能玩旋转木马。 招财猫寺庙。 浅草寺的房檐。 晴空塔旁边真的很拥 […]",
  "content": "<p>蓄谋已久的日本之行。</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>东京</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2897-d5c7-4b38-9db7-e58bb135e0c7.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>迪士尼遇到大雨，只能玩旋转木马。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2928-e400-4103-a9e3-6553cbd82f0a.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>招财猫寺庙。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2a8d-afd1-4ffc-abcf-0349df958c48.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>浅草寺的房檐。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2937-6212-462e-8151-4d407c7574a1.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>晴空塔旁边真的很拥挤，我甚至找不到地方给它拍一张正面照。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2939-3a4a-48fd-8812-3927dc2fb665.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>庭园美术馆很漂亮，蚊子也不少。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2946-183e-4c3e-8d9d-feaa73bdf4c6.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>TeamLab Planets还是不错的。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa294b-085e-43eb-b7e2-34da1090be11.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>贡献了很多抽象照片。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2951-6c2c-484a-ae81-95d54bc655df.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>灯光实在太暗，拍人有点麻烦。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2956-68fb-4cff-8cb5-6a84b847adb9.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>一个充满了气球的房间。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2956-36a4-4678-b354-40b703a4d355.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>气球颜色随着灯光颜色改变。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2978-7b83-4fc9-b85f-5caafbb4b256.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>东京铁塔的正面照要跑到旁边摩天大楼的观景台才能拍到。</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>京都</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2898-5d9f-4f7a-a798-9e3f0df39727.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>跑到京都看寺庙。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2897-3944-4b74-8b59-2d8eb93ba9e4.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>做工精美，配色鲜艳。但是似乎设计都有模板，逛了好几个，大同小异。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28af-4dee-4587-9a2c-472bb6947ca0.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>清水寺有点不一样。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28b4-48ce-4588-91e2-2e73ad2b8d1c.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>感觉这些塔普遍头重脚轻。上面很宏伟，但是到底部就显得很朴素。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28bb-a47a-4ce1-a82b-457927144b49.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>锐角的房檐也很有特色。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28bb-d230-4c80-9b1a-c4604a5e73b0.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>人不是一般的多，所以拍了很多抽象照片。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28c4-3cc1-485f-89dd-a65f0ca8dc5c.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>各色绳子。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28ca-63b6-49a2-a883-29cb196d09a1.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>清水寺好鲜艳。现在的审美看起来还是不过时。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28cc-588b-4b77-8ca2-976d1d5e56eb.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>很多石塔。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28db-c445-4891-9419-7a29d5cb0c68.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>千本鸟居我来了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28df-655e-4f80-9abf-48768e420cfd.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>金红配色很古典。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28e9-e6c5-4800-b15e-e67138342159.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>朝圣千本鸟居。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28e7-bfbb-4aa1-8116-afe3e3c0f236.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>或许真的有一千个，总之我是没走完。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28f0-7793-4453-ada5-55a5163a3229.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>商店街里也有神社。</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>大阪</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28d6-8639-4d89-bd0c-06c8b7277d08.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>大阪城全是人，照片里都看得到。</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>名古屋</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa28f1-fff5-4132-930b-7d6a7f952486.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>名古屋水族馆。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2900-a881-4896-b55a-385eb2280e4f.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>水族馆很大，至少比奥克兰的大。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2902-2c0c-4b03-a4e9-38efb9f94c3e.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>水母很可爱，透明的身体。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2909-7f4e-472c-9425-62e62d6855a9.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>还有企鹅。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa290c-765b-4818-9510-375591537a30.webp?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>还有很抽象的水。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2918-11cd-4c6d-bdfb-b3a69b411a16.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>可爱的花园鳗。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa291c-4d41-4701-b05f-3e257b29f2c3.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>港口又忙碌又艺术。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/9ffa2923-8092-41c4-9ea7-f6cbdcbdc43c.webp?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>名古屋电视塔。</p>",
